{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-projects-post-jsx","path":"/project/coronaunity/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"name":"Alan Hutcheson","title":"Alan Hutcheson | Full-Stack Developer & Platform Engineer","description":"Experienced full stack developer and platform engineer looking for work in climate & sustainability technology","about":"Technical lead with 5 years experience working across the technology stack; from full stack web and mobile development to functional automation testing, performance testing and dev-ops and infrastructure work. Passionate about designing and building applications and technologies that can help provide real world social value, particularly in the climate change space. Worked on a range of project scales and technologies, from solo freelance mobile development to large scale critical public sector infrastructure projects.","author":null,"resume":"https://drive.google.com/file/d/15vdIkCfZirUI_uYamJpfW_w85HPl2ab0/view?usp=sharing","github":"https://github.com/AlanPedro","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/alan-p-hutcheson/"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bf72a424-f2aa-5545-aa6c-85576d81bd94","excerpt":"The Context During lockdown I joined Helpful Engineering, a community of engineers and designers that had come together at the start of the COVID lockdown toâ€¦","html":"<h2>The Context</h2>\n<p>During lockdown I joined Helpful Engineering, a community of engineers and designers that had come together at the start of the COVID lockdown to build tools and services to help those in need.</p>\n<p>I was then approached by a student-run charity called CoronaUnity who were looking for a developer to support them with their Phone a Friend Service.</p>\n<h2>What was the problem being solved?</h2>\n<p>Lockdown left many people completely socially isolated, impacting their wellbeing and mental health. They were just looking for someone to talk to, to give them that social contact that they were missing. </p>\n<h2>What was the Phone a Friend service?</h2>\n<p>The service was a platform whereby:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>volunteers could sign up to offer their free time to chat</li>\n<li>people who were feeling isolated and wanted to speak to someone could sign up to request a phone call from a volunteer</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Users and volunteers would be matched based on their preferences and availability</p>\n<h2>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Matching based on preferences (gender, from a member of a charity)</li>\n<li>2 hour time slots from 8am to 10pm every day</li>\n<li>Text and email notifications for successful matches and an alert once the phone call had started</li>\n<li>Phone numbers anonymised</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>What was my role?</h2>\n<p>I architected the whole service and was responsible for all the backend functionality. Another team were working on the front end website and sign up form.</p>\n<h2>Technology Stack</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Firebase Cloud Function (Node + Typescript): <em>Run all our backend logic, the matching function, sending texts, alerts and connecting calls</em></li>\n<li>Twilio: <em>Handling calls, connecting calls and sending texts</em></li>\n<li>Sendgrid: <em>Sending emails</em></li>\n<li>Slack: <em>For pro-active alerting and monitoring</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Code coming soon - I just need to remove old secrets etc.</em></p>\n<h3>Solution Design</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; margin: 0 0 30px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/devfolio/static/1b898bd45395b75b38f7e9f23776819c/ca12d/CoronaUnityPAFArchitecture.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.32432432432432%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Phone a Friend Service Solution Design\"\n        title=\"Phone a Friend Service Solution Design\"\n        src=\"/devfolio/static/1b898bd45395b75b38f7e9f23776819c/fcda8/CoronaUnityPAFArchitecture.png\"\n        srcset=\"/devfolio/static/1b898bd45395b75b38f7e9f23776819c/12f09/CoronaUnityPAFArchitecture.png 148w,\n/devfolio/static/1b898bd45395b75b38f7e9f23776819c/e4a3f/CoronaUnityPAFArchitecture.png 295w,\n/devfolio/static/1b898bd45395b75b38f7e9f23776819c/fcda8/CoronaUnityPAFArchitecture.png 590w,\n/devfolio/static/1b898bd45395b75b38f7e9f23776819c/ca12d/CoronaUnityPAFArchitecture.png 647w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Matching Function Flow</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 521px; margin: 0 0 30px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/devfolio/static/abe5601425c9db0978bdeee410d91b1c/bb9c5/CoronaUnityPAFMatcherFunction.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 92.56756756756756%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Phone a Friend Service Matching Function\"\n        title=\"Phone a Friend Service Matching Function\"\n        src=\"/devfolio/static/abe5601425c9db0978bdeee410d91b1c/bb9c5/CoronaUnityPAFMatcherFunction.png\"\n        srcset=\"/devfolio/static/abe5601425c9db0978bdeee410d91b1c/12f09/CoronaUnityPAFMatcherFunction.png 148w,\n/devfolio/static/abe5601425c9db0978bdeee410d91b1c/e4a3f/CoronaUnityPAFMatcherFunction.png 295w,\n/devfolio/static/abe5601425c9db0978bdeee410d91b1c/bb9c5/CoronaUnityPAFMatcherFunction.png 521w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 521px) 100vw, 521px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Matching Function Flow</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 570px; margin: 0 0 30px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/devfolio/static/2bc353a340930af98c08e6edb6a278ba/432e7/CoronaUnityPAFHandleCallerFunction.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 107.43243243243244%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Phone a Friend Service Handle Call Function\"\n        title=\"Phone a Friend Service Handle Call Function\"\n        src=\"/devfolio/static/2bc353a340930af98c08e6edb6a278ba/432e7/CoronaUnityPAFHandleCallerFunction.png\"\n        srcset=\"/devfolio/static/2bc353a340930af98c08e6edb6a278ba/12f09/CoronaUnityPAFHandleCallerFunction.png 148w,\n/devfolio/static/2bc353a340930af98c08e6edb6a278ba/e4a3f/CoronaUnityPAFHandleCallerFunction.png 295w,\n/devfolio/static/2bc353a340930af98c08e6edb6a278ba/432e7/CoronaUnityPAFHandleCallerFunction.png 570w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Outcome</h2>\n<p>We ran the service for 3 months (May - August 2020), matching just over 300 users over this time period. The feedback from users was overwhelmingly positive, however we struggled to get funding to suppor the platform costs and as lockdown restrictions started to ease up in the summer, CoronaUnity decided to focus on other projects and ended up discontinuing the Phone a Friend service.</p>\n<!-- ## Challenges we faced -->","frontmatter":{"title":"CoronaUnity - Phone a Friend Service","date":"October 01, 2020","description":"A service connecting volunteers with those left isolated during the COVID lockdown of 2020."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/project/coronaunity/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/project/carbn/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Carbn"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/project/cemt/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Carbon Emissions Measurement Tool"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}